				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\ge$$\end{document}≥ 200 m) and smoking status, we will test the interaction between these factors and treatment assignment to determine if the treatment effect is different for patients across the baseline MWD stratum.
